      <li>
        <q>¿Cuáles preguntas les ayudaron a encontrar cuántas sillas había en la habitación?</q>  (How many chairs were in the corner? How many chairs were in each row? How many rows were there?)
      </li>
      <li>If there were any questions that the data card cannot answer, discuss them here.</li>
    </ul>
